==English==
===Etymology===
From ''[[im]]'' + ''[[practicable]]''

===Noun===
'''impracticable'''
# An unmanageable person.

===Adjective===
{{en-adj-more}}
# Not [[practicable]]; impossible or difficult in [[practice]].
# Of a passage or road: [[impassable]].
# Of a person or thing: [[unmanageable]].

====Translations====
